1.10	Vandicholai_Chinraasu	Vandicholai Chinraasu	Vandicholai Chinraasu is a 1994 Tamil film directed by Manoj Kumar. This remains the only Sathyaraj movie where A R Rahman composed the music. This movie was directed by Manoj Kumar. It was released on Tamil New Year Day. The film received mixed reviews from the box office.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ea/Album_vandicholaichinraasu_cover.jpg/220px-Album_vandicholaichinraasu_cover.jpg
